    "body": "Found a workaround, using selfdestructing contract: \r\n\r\n```\r\npragma solidity 0.6.12;\r\n\r\ncontract SelfdestructTransfer {\r\n  function destroyAndTransfer(address payable to) external payable {\r\n    selfdestruct(to);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```",
